### What I found beyond the (empty) reviewer report:

- **z-index chaos**: ClickToStart at 9999, Tooltip at 10, VirtualKeyboard at 1/2 -- all bypass the token system that was just built in cycle 1
- **CrossOriginError is a token-free zone**: 3 hardcoded hex colors, 5 hardcoded pixel values
- **Empty panels are the first impression**: New users see blank canvas in arrangement, blank piano roll, empty mixer -- no guidance anywhere
- **No heading hierarchy**: Screen readers have zero navigation landmarks beyond a single HEADER region
- **Select primitive is half-finished**: Has no disabled styling while Button does
- **Safari AudioContext fragility**: Single-attempt resume with no retry
- **Tooltip renders behind everything**: z-index: 10 when contextMenu is 700
